Package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.select

Interface Select

public interface Select
Represents a selectable component, typically an HTML 'select' or similar UI element that supports selecting multiple options. Provides methods to select options by text or strategy, retrieve available or selected options, and check visibility or enabled states.

Implementations commonly rely on Selenium-based operations using container elements (SmartWebElement) or locators (By). This interface standardizes how select widgets are handled, regardless of the underlying framework or implementation.

Usage ranges from simple dropdown selects to more complex multi-select scenarios. The selectOptions() methods allow specifying multiple values or applying a Strategy for custom selection logic.
